[DhtmlXQ_comment0]mg clog am jqqq g095||Black is threatening with a kill with R7+1.||Red's attacking forces seem to be disorganized and the black cannon and horse seem capable of defending against against the palcorner horse checkmate. How can red win?||||====||||Tactic: Clog ?? 01||||The Clog ??  is the tactic discussed here. ||In Xiangqi, the king is confined to the parameters of the palace. There are basically 9 points where it can move. When you are able to limit or clog up the palace, thereby limiting the number of places where the king can move, you would be able to perform a kill swiftly. To do so, sacrificing your own pieces is often needed. A final check from a chariot, horse, cannon or even the humble pawn is all that is needed for a smothered checkmate.[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
